they're not decomposed

00:43:43.350 --> 00:43:45.150 align:middle line:10%
before getting there.

00:43:45.150 --> 00:43:47.710 align:middle line:10%
That's deeper than
one kilometer.

00:43:47.710 --> 00:43:49.650 align:middle line:10%
Then we talk about
it being sequestered

00:43:49.650 --> 00:43:54.150 align:middle line:10%
for considerable time scales,
like several centuries.

00:43:54.150 --> 00:43:55.950 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow, really, really exciting.

00:43:55.950 --> 00:43:57.480 align:middle line:90%
That's fantastic, Dorte.

00:43:57.480 --> 00:44:01.590 align:middle line:84%
Dorte thinks that 173 million
tons of seaweed carbon

00:44:01.590 --> 00:44:04.600 align:middle line:84%
