way into the deep ocean,

00:44:12.732 --> 00:44:14.190 align:middle line:84%
and that the carbon
in that seaweed

00:44:14.190 --> 00:44:18.132 align:middle line:84%
is staying down there out of
the atmospheric carbon cycle.

00:44:18.132 --> 00:44:19.590 align:middle line:84%
I guess the big
thing we don't know

00:44:19.590 --> 00:44:21.510 align:middle line:84%
is, if we do this on
an industrial scale

00:44:21.510 --> 00:44:24.770 align:middle line:84%
and grow seaweed farms that are
transporting lots of seaweed

00:44:24.770 --> 00:44:28.170 align:middle line:84%
into the deep oceans, what the
consequence of that will be.

00:44:28.170 --> 00:44:30.826 align:middle line:84%
We won't know till
we try it, I guess.

